{
  "id": "censure-road-camp-maev",
  "title": "Sutler Judith",
  "nodes": {
    "start": {
      "lines": [
        "Sutler Judith keeps her cart angled so every guard must walk around it.",
        "\"Officially I sell comfort goods. Unofficially, comfort now includes ammunition and beans that do not argue back.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Collect the graveyard censure bundle",
          "conditions": {
            "flags": [
              "heard-bell-resolved-censure",
              "heard-bell-censure-report-filed",
              "heard-bell-censure-report-acknowledged"
            ],
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-censure-reward-claimed"
            ]
          },
          "next": "heard-bell-censure-reward"
        },
        {
          "label": "Collect Aquila's issue bundle",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "censure-road-voss-report-perfect",
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "censure-road-voss-report-rewarded"
            ]
          },
          "next": "voss-report-reward"
        },
        {
          "label": "Trade with Judith",
          "effects": {
            "trade": "censure-sutler-maev"
          }
        },
        {
          "label": "Ask what the road is saying",
          "next": "road"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the cart",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "road": {
      "lines": [
        "\"The Hallowfen wagons stopped paying in coin and started paying in reasons.\"",
        "\"Reasons spoil faster than fish. I stopped taking them.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Collect the graveyard censure bundle",
          "conditions": {
            "flags": [
              "heard-bell-resolved-censure",
              "heard-bell-censure-report-filed",
              "heard-bell-censure-report-acknowledged"
            ],
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-censure-reward-claimed"
            ]
          },
          "next": "heard-bell-censure-reward"
        },
        {
          "label": "Collect Aquila's issue bundle",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "censure-road-voss-report-perfect",
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "censure-road-voss-report-rewarded"
            ]
          },
          "next": "voss-report-reward"
        },
        {
          "label": "Trade with Judith",
          "effects": {
            "trade": "censure-sutler-maev"
          }
        },
        {
          "label": "Ask about her back-room figures",
          "conditions": {
            "flagsAtLeast": {
              "count": 1,
              "of": [
                "censure-road-sutler-dropped-tally-found",
                "censure-road-sutler-false-price-mark-found"
              ]
            }
          },
          "next": "back-room"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the cart",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "back-room": {
      "lines": [
        "Judith shifts until her shoulder blocks the cart door.",
        "\"Back-room figures cost more because they know where I sleep. Choose the mark you came to argue over.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Show her the hidden porter tally",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "censure-road-sutler-dropped-tally-found",
            "flagsAbsent": ["censure-road-maev-dropped-tally-reported"]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "censure-road-maev-dropped-tally-reported",
            "log": "Judith keeps the porter tally and marks the double sale for correction."
          },
          "next": "dropped-tally"
        },
        {
          "label": "Rub out the added price stroke",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "censure-road-sutler-false-price-mark-found",
            "flagsAbsent": ["censure-road-maev-price-mark-reported"]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "censure-road-maev-price-mark-reported",
            "log": "Judith restores the camp price on the crate that never moved."
          },
          "next": "price-mark"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the back-room figures",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "dropped-tally": {
      "lines": [
        "Judith reads the porter strip against the grain, where the missing road name left a fresh cut.",
        "\"One crate sold twice is theft with a receipt. Leave me the strip; I know how close this porter trims to a number.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Leave her the porter strip",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "price-mark": {
      "lines": [
        "Judith wets her thumb and wipes away the added chalk stroke. The lower price returns.",
        "\"Camp price buys what is on the peg. Road price buys what may not reach the next peg. This crate never moved, so the extra stroke comes off.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Leave the corrected price",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "voss-report-reward": {
      "lines": [
        "\"Aquila sent a slate with your name on it. She wrote impressed, then scratched until the word looked less dangerous.\"",
        "\"Orders say I hand over a ribguard, one dressing, and two rounds from my own shelf. I will mourn with dignity after you leave.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Take the free gear",
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "censure-road-voss-report-rewarded",
            "inventory": {
              "add": [
                {
                  "item": "camp-issue-ribguard",
                  "count": 1
                },
                {
                  "item": "field-dressing",
                  "count": 1
                },
                {
                  "item": "relic-rounds",
                  "count": 2
                }
              ]
            },
            "log": "Judith gives you Aquila's issue bundle."
          },
          "close": true
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the bundle for now",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "heard-bell-censure-reward": {
      "lines": [
        "Judith checks Aquila's black seal, then sets a paper writ beneath three cartridges so the wind cannot take it.",
        "\"Ten ducats, one dressing, and a burn writ. The rounds are not a sermon. Put them where the writ fails.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Take the censure bundle",
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-censure-reward-claimed",
            "inventory": {
              "add": [
                {
                  "item": "road-purgation-writ",
                  "count": 1
                },
                {
                  "item": "relic-rounds",
                  "count": 3
                },
                {
                  "item": "field-dressing",
                  "count": 1
                },
                {
                  "item": "ducat",
                  "count": 10
                }
              ]
            },
            "log": "Judith issues the graveyard censure bundle."
          },
          "close": true
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the bundle with Judith",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
